  <brief_title>Acute Gastric Variceal Bleeding: Endoscopic Treatment Versus BRTO</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Endoscopic Cyanoacrylate Injection Versus Balloon-occluded Retrograde Transvenous Obliteration in the Management of Acute Gastric Variceal Bleeding</official_title>
