  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to study the efficacy of endoscopic cyanoacrylate injection
      versus balloon-occluded retrograde transvenous obliteration in the management of acute
      gastric bleeding.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
